imdb.plot outline: The television series that will chronicle the marriage of Qianlong Emperor and the Step Empress, Ru Yi Ulanara. Starring Xun Zhou and Wallace Huo, the series is based on an online novel Empresses in the Palace (2011) by Liu Lianzi (Xuelan Wu), and is the sequel to the critically acclaimed drama Empresses in the Palace. It airs on Tencent Video starting August 20, 2018.
imdb.title: Ruyi's Royal Love in the Palace
plot: Chronicle the marriage of Qianlong Emperor and the Step Empress, Ru Yi Ulanara.

The television series that will chronicle the marriage of Qianlong Emperor and the Step Empress, Ru Yi Ulanara. Starring 'Xun Zhou' (qv) and 'Wallace Huo' (qv), the series is based on an online novel _Zhen Huan Zhuan (2011)_ (qv) by Liu Lianzi ('Xuelan Wu' (qv)), and is the sequel to the critically acclaimed drama Empresses in the Palace. It airs on Tencent Video starting August 20, 2018.::Ellie's Wonder
